00:23:59,445 --> 00:24:00,286
or watching a streamer.

541
00:24:00,867 --> 00:24:05,190
But strategies that are very, very slow and grindy,

542
00:24:06,171 --> 00:24:06,311
like

543
00:24:07,082 --> 00:24:10,123
