00:24:18,748 --> 00:24:20,249
but it's really, really boring.

550
00:24:20,589 --> 00:24:21,410
Those are the kind of things

551
00:24:21,430 --> 00:24:22,871
that we wanted to nuke the hardest.

552
00:24:23,511 --> 00:24:24,592
Instead of something where you see

553
00:24:24,632 --> 00:24:26,333
like a really big number on the screen,

554
00:24:26,373 --> 00:24:28,554
you feel really powerful, those are feel good

555
00:24:28,594 --> 00:24:29,915
and that's what we wanted to encourage.

556
00:24:29,935 --> 00:24:30,815
Thanks.

